## User Flows

### Flow A — OTP Login (Passwordless)

```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    participant FE as Frontend
    participant BE as Backend
    participant N as Email/WhatsApp

    FE->>BE: POST /api/auth/request-otp { identifier }
    BE->>N: Send 6-digit OTP
    BE-->>FE: { status: "success", message: "OTP sent" }
    FE->>FE: Show OTP input screen
    FE->>BE: POST /api/auth/verify-otp-login { identifier, otp }
    BE-->>FE: { status: "success", data: { token, ...user } }
    FE->>FE: Store token → redirect to dashboard
```

### Flow B — Registration + Email/Phone Verification

```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    participant FE as Frontend
    participant BE as Backend
    participant N as Email/WhatsApp

    FE->>BE: POST /api/auth/register { name, email, password, phoneNo }
    BE->>N: Send Email OTP + WhatsApp OTP
    BE-->>FE: { status: "success", data: { token, ...user } }
    FE->>FE: Show "Verify your email" screen
    FE->>BE: POST /api/auth/verify-email { code } (with JWT)
    BE-->>FE: { status: "success", message: "Email verified" }
    FE->>FE: Show "Verify your phone" screen
    FE->>BE: POST /api/auth/verify-phone { code } (with JWT)
    BE-->>FE: { status: "success", message: "Phone verified" }
    FE->>FE: Redirect to dashboard
```

